taunovo/status/2067568066024595852", "text": "Japan's Cosmo Energy to keep Middle East crude focus despite Iran war #oott https://t.co/yf7PIv3MNz", "time": "11:20", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6546, "likes": 12, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067574823124123984", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2067574823124123984", "text": "Shoutout to this beautiful peace. Dropping the SAR radar feed today on June 18th—we're seeing some vessel prints picking up east of the SoH. It’s nowhere near normal flow velocity, but at least five hulls are making way. Looks like they’re hugging the Iranian corridor.\n\n#oott #iran", "time": "11:47", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 18490, "likes": 131, "replies": 8, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067596746914398672", "url": "https://x.com/garquake/status/2067596746914398672", "text": "Another day of markets ripping and oil tanking in pre market - must be wierd having this wild perception of what we think is happening and what is actually happening for some - Crazy how our personal biases especially ownership enhances our beliefs and clouds reality #oott https://t.co/UBayotV4F7", "time": "13:14", "author": "garquake", "author_name": "Burnsco", "followers": 32104, "views": 4093, "likes": 39, "replies": 7, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067602699260997784", "url": "https://x.com/GregaHorvatFX/status/2067602699260997784", "text": "$XOM came nicely down, lost 15% from that a-bc- completed correction.\n\nand I think there is room for more, I guess you know where resistance is if we rebound, and what that means for crude. \n\n#Elliottwave #OOTT #oil https://t.co/XQbZC74Wq8", "time": "13:37", "author": "GregaHorvatFX", "author_name": "Grega Horvat", "followers": 36699, "views": 4550, "likes": 25, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067605700193271819", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2067605700193271819", "text": "Another massive binary option (Sep Brt $70 put) traded for 100 million barrels (!!!) in one go as a stark reminder of the hidden power of OTC oil markets.\nTheir pricing is highly sensitive to the shape of the vol skew (see more in the book/YouTube channel).\n#oott https://t.co/Qi3vaS1reY", "time": "13:49", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 8099, "likes": 30, "replies": 7, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067610952972066862", "url": "https://x.com/diepthaolong/status/2067610952972066862", "text": "Price touched the lower boundary of the green box and got weak reactions, it’s clearly that we’re going a bit lower.\nMaybe it would find the bottom around $71.8 - $66.48\n\n#oott #WTI", "time": "14:10", "author": "diepthaolong", "author_name": "Viv", "followers": 443, "views": 3081, "likes": 17, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067625766234595733", "url": "https://x.com/UnintendedCons5/status/2067625766234595733", "text": "Will Iran give up its nuclear program or nuclear material in a final agreement?\n\n#oott", "time": "15:09", "author": "UnintendedCons5", "author_name": "Unintended Consequence", "followers": 6067, "views": 4251, "likes": 3, "replies": 4, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067634983410507979", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067634983410507979", "text": "The risks behind the Iran-US breakthrough https://t.co/ZE8MPQOYcA #OOTT #US #IranWar‌", "time": "15:46", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 7342, "likes": 35, "replies": 3, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067637281733664968", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067637281733664968", "text": "We feel quite confident that we can temporarily lift those (#Iran) sanctions without going to Congress and seeking their approval on that - Vance #oott", "time": "15:55", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 13688, "likes": 24, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067666416853999733", "url": "https://x.com/bencahillenergy/status/2067666416853999733", "text": "What's needed for normal Strait of Hormuz transit to resume? Check out Intertanko's list of concerns. Link below. #oil #iran #oott https://t.co/MSCFt0XHP3", "time": "17:51", "author": "bencahillenergy", "author_name": "Ben Cahill", "followers": 4194, "views": 1544, "likes": 13, "replies": 4, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067670631903281455", "url": "https://x.com/refineryritolia/status/2067670631903281455", "text": "India resuming purchases of Iranian crude and LPG soon is still \"too\" early to call. Several nuanced technical and economic factors need to be addressed first. However, given the current pace of Russian oil loadings, Russia is expected to remain India's major supplier. #oott", "time": "18:07", "author": "refineryritolia", "author_name": "Sumit Ritolia", "followers": 402, "views": 10006, "likes": 6, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067678551676256386", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067678551676256386", "text": "3 Saudi VLCCs carrying around 6 million barrels of crude have transited the Strait, reappearing on AIS after more than two months. @Kpler #OOTT", "time": "18:39", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 11525, "likes": 102, "replies": 4, "retweets": 21, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067710356344963261", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2067710356344963261", "text": "Iran Video #14 - Obvi